definitions.definition: A short , sharp or high note or noise, as of a bird or insect .
A pulse of signal whose frequency sweeps through a band of frequencies for the duration of the pulse.

main_definition: A short , sharp or high note or noise, as of a bird or insect .
secondary_definitions: ( radar , sonar , radio telescopy etc. ) A pulse of signal whose frequency sweeps through a band of frequencies for the duration of the pulse.
